1. Call Preprocessor with the topic as parameter

javac Preprocessor.java
java Preprocessor $@

e.g. java Preprocessor 孩子

2. Call findZHchar.py to find chinese charcters in documents
./findZHchar.py

3. Call createData which will create input data 
which are required for lda
./createData.py

4. Finally call lda.sh
You can change the parameters as you like.
./lda.sh

5. Check the result in /results
topic_zh.txt
